responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "7E21D47441D6EE53F0FDEC9F6E2B4180", "I knew you looked savvy. Strider Owens and I can\'t agree on what to do about the bandits between here and the coast. I may not be your boss, but I\'m begging you: just fix it. Grayshore can pay.")
